  <entry>
    <title>创建个人博客 by GitHub.io</title>
    <link href="/2021/12/05/CreateBlog/"/>
    <url>/2021/12/05/CreateBlog/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Quick-Start"><a href="#Quick-Start" class="headerlink" title="Quick Start"></a>Quick Start</h2><h3 id="配置Github"><a href="#配置Github" class="headerlink" title="配置Github"></a>配置Github</h3><h4 id="创建仓库"><a href="#创建仓库" class="headerlink" title="创建仓库"></a>创建仓库</h4><p>仓库名字为 github 用户名.github.io</p><h4 id="生成SSH-key"><a href="#生成SSH-key" class="headerlink" title="生成SSH key"></a>生成SSH key</h4><ol><li><p>ssh-keygen -t rsa -C “GitHub注册邮箱”</p></li><li><p>ssh <a href="mailto:&#x67;&#x69;&#116;&#x40;&#x67;&#105;&#x74;&#104;&#x75;&#x62;&#46;&#99;&#111;&#109;">&#x67;&#x69;&#116;&#x40;&#x67;&#105;&#x74;&#104;&#x75;&#x62;&#46;&#99;&#111;&#109;</a></p><p> 如果出现The authenticity of host xx can’t be established</p><p> 输入yes</p></li><li><p>进入~/.ssh 中复制 id_rsa.pub文件内容</p></li><li><p>头像 - setting - SSH and GPG keys</p></li><li><p>Title可以随意填，将复制的内容添加进Key</p></li></ol><h3 id="安装node"><a href="#安装node" class="headerlink" title="安装node"></a>安装node</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ brew install node<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/server.html">Server</a></p><h3 id="安装Hexo"><a href="#安装Hexo" class="headerlink" title="安装Hexo"></a>安装Hexo</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ npm install -g hexo-cli <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="配置博客"><a href="#配置博客" class="headerlink" title="配置博客"></a>配置博客</h3><p>新建Blog文件夹</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ hexo init blog //初始化文件夹<br>$ hexo g//生成<br>$ hexo s//启动服务预览<br>$ hexo d//部署<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="将配置好的博客推送到github中"><a href="#将配置好的博客推送到github中" class="headerlink" title="将配置好的博客推送到github中"></a>将配置好的博客推送到github中</h3><h4 id="修改配置文件"><a href="#修改配置文件" class="headerlink" title="修改配置文件"></a>修改配置文件</h4><p>打开根目录下的_config.yml</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs xml">deploy:<br>  type: &#x27;git&#x27;<br>  repo: ssh<br>  branch: main<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="保存站点配置文件"><a href="#保存站点配置文件" class="headerlink" title="保存站点配置文件"></a>保存站点配置文件</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ npm install hexo-deployer-git --save<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="更改主题"><a href="#更改主题" class="headerlink" title="更改主题"></a>更改主题</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ <span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span> hexo-site<br>$ npm install hexo-theme-next<br>//再修改配置文件中的<br>theme: next<br><br>$ hexo clean <br>$ hexo g <br>$ hexo d<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><!--简化操作--><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">hexo cl&amp;&amp;hexo g&amp;&amp;hexo d <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
  <entry>
    <title>动态代理</title>
    <link href="/2021/12/04/%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/"/>
    <url>/2021/12/04/%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="静态代理："><a href="#静态代理：" class="headerlink" title="静态代理："></a>静态代理：</h2><p>静态代理实现过程</p><p>当一个接口有很多实现类时，那么为每一个实现类都可能需要去写一个代理类，工程量会很大</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">interface</span> <span class="hljs-title">Speaker</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">speak</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span>;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title">Zhangsan</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">implements</span> <span class="hljs-title">Speaker</span></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-meta">@Override</span><br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">speak</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>        System.out.println(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;张三：我老婆打我(原有的功能)&quot;</span>);<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title">ZhangSanLawyer</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">implements</span> <span class="hljs-title">Speaker</span></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">private</span> Zhangsan zhangsan = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> Zhangsan();<br><br>    <span class="hljs-meta">@Override</span><br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">speak</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>        System.out.println(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;律师：引用法律条文(功能增强)&quot;</span>);<br>        zhangsan.speak();<br>        System.out.println(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;律师：道德不允许家暴(功能增强)&quot;</span>);<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title">Fating</span></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">(String[] args)</span> </span>&#123;<br>        Speaker speaker = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> ZhangSanLawyer();<br>        speaker.speak();<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="什么是动态代理？"><a href="#什么是动态代理？" class="headerlink" title="什么是动态代理？"></a>什么是动态代理？</h2><p>a类想访问b类，但是不能直接访问，所以需要一个代理帮助a类访问b类</p><p>a                —–c—–&gt;                 b</p><h2 id="代理的作用"><a href="#代理的作用" class="headerlink" title="代理的作用"></a>代理的作用</h2><ol><li>功能增强：不改变自身的情况下，添加更多的功能    </li><li>访问控制：代理类能够让你不能访问目标类</li></ol><h2 id="实现代理的方式"><a href="#实现代理的方式" class="headerlink" title="实现代理的方式"></a>实现代理的方式</h2><ol><li><p>静态代理</p><p> 代理类通过自己手动实现，同时代理的目标类是确定的</p> <!-- 特点：实现简单，容易理解 --></li><li><p>JDK动态代理 (必须实现接口)</p> <figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> java.lang.reflect.InvocationHandler;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> java.lang.reflect.Method;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> java.lang.reflect.Proxy;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">/**</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> * ClassName: ProxyDemo &lt;br/&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> * Description: &lt;br/&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> * date: 2021/12/4 8:33 下午&lt;br/&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> *</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> * <span class="hljs-doctag">@author</span> wang &lt;br/&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> * <span class="hljs-doctag">@since</span> JDK 1.8</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> */</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title">ProxyDemo</span> </span>&#123;<br><br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">interface</span> <span class="hljs-title">Speaker</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">speak</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span>;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title">LawyerProxy</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">implements</span> <span class="hljs-title">InvocationHandler</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-comment">/**</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">    动态代理</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     */</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">private</span> Object object;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-title">LawyerProxy</span><span class="hljs-params">(Object object)</span> </span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>.object = object;<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-meta">@Override</span><br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> Object <span class="hljs-title">invoke</span><span class="hljs-params">(Object proxy, Method method, Object[] args)</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">throws</span> Throwable </span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;speak&quot;</span>.equals(method.getName()))&#123;<br>            System.out.println(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;律师：引用法律条文(功能增强)&quot;</span>);<br>            <span class="hljs-comment">//反射</span><br>            method.invoke(object, args);<br>            System.out.println(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;律师：道德不允许家暴(功能增强)&quot;</span>);<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">null</span>;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title">Zhangsan</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">implements</span> <span class="hljs-title">Speaker</span></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-meta">@Override</span><br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">speak</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>        System.out.println(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;张三：我老婆打我(原有的功能)&quot;</span>);<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title">Fating</span></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">(String[] args)</span> </span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-comment">//动态代理</span><br>        LawyerProxy lawyerProxy = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> LawyerProxy(<span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> Zhangsan());<br>        Speaker speaker1 = (Speaker) Proxy.newProxyInstance(Fating.class.getClassLoader(),<br>                <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> Class[]&#123;Speaker.class&#125;,<br>                lawyerProxy);<br>        speaker1.speak();<br>    &#125;   <br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>CGLib动态代理 (不要求实现接口)</p></li></ol>]]></content>
    
    
    
