  <entry>
    <title>Mysql笔记</title>
    <link href="/2021/09/26/mysql%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/"/>
    <url>/2021/09/26/mysql%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="安装mysql"><a href="#安装mysql" class="headerlink" title="安装mysql"></a>安装mysql</h2><ol><li><p>brew install mysql</p></li><li><p>官网下载dmg安装包</p><p> <a href="https://dev.mysql.com/downloads/">https://dev.mysql.com/downloads/</a></p></li></ol><h2 id="启动-停止-重启"><a href="#启动-停止-重启" class="headerlink" title="启动 停止 重启"></a>启动 停止 重启</h2><h2 id="登陆"><a href="#登陆" class="headerlink" title="登陆"></a>登陆</h2><h3 id="启动"><a href="#启动" class="headerlink" title="启动"></a>启动</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ mysql.server start<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="停止"><a href="#停止" class="headerlink" title="停止"></a>停止</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ mysql.server stop<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="重启"><a href="#重启" class="headerlink" title="重启"></a>重启</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ mysql.server restart<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="登陆-1"><a href="#登陆-1" class="headerlink" title="登陆"></a>登陆</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ mysql -u root -p<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="数据库语法"><a href="#数据库语法" class="headerlink" title="数据库语法"></a>数据库语法</h2><h3 id="创建和查看数据库"><a href="#创建和查看数据库" class="headerlink" title="创建和查看数据库"></a>创建和查看数据库</h3><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">create</span> database datebase_name;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">show</span> databases;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="创建表"><a href="#创建表" class="headerlink" title="创建表"></a>创建表</h3><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">create</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">table</span> table_name(<br>Field1 type1 <span class="hljs-keyword">null</span> key <span class="hljs-keyword">default</span> extra,<br>Field2 type2 <span class="hljs-keyword">null</span> key <span class="hljs-keyword">default</span> extra<br>例如:<br>(Ssex enum(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;男&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;女&#x27;</span>)).<br>)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="查看表"><a href="#查看表" class="headerlink" title="查看表"></a>查看表</h3><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">desc</span> table_name<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="查询信息"><a href="#查询信息" class="headerlink" title="查询信息"></a>查询信息</h3><h4 id="基本框架"><a href="#基本框架" class="headerlink" title="基本框架"></a>基本框架</h4><p>Select （如需去重，distinct）列<br>From 表（如需多表数据，表1，表2，表3）<br>Where 行（多表结合后，数据会乱序增多，所以则需要增加限制条件，即观察多表的相同项，进行限定）</p><h5 id="例子"><a href="#例子" class="headerlink" title="例子"></a>例子</h5><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">select</span> studentname （选择列）<br><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> course,grade,student （选择表）<br><span class="hljs-keyword">where</span> student.studentid<span class="hljs-operator">=</span>grade.studentid<br><span class="hljs-keyword">and</span> course.courseid<span class="hljs-operator">=</span>grade.courseid<br><span class="hljs-keyword">and</span> coursename<span class="hljs-operator">=</span><span class="hljs-string">&#x27;JAVA程序设计&#x27;</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">and</span> grade＞<span class="hljs-operator">=</span><span class="hljs-number">60</span><span class="hljs-keyword">and</span> grade＜<span class="hljs-operator">=</span><span class="hljs-number">70</span>(<span class="hljs-keyword">between</span> <span class="hljs-number">60</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">and</span> <span class="hljs-number">70</span>)<br>（限定条件）<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="case-then"><a href="#case-then" class="headerlink" title="case then"></a>case then</h4><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">case</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">when</span> 情况<span class="hljs-number">1</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">then</span> 结果<span class="hljs-number">1</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">when</span> 情况<span class="hljs-number">2</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">then</span> 结果<span class="hljs-number">2</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> 结果<span class="hljs-number">3</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">end</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="排序"><a href="#排序" class="headerlink" title="排序"></a>排序</h4><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">order</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">by</span> 排序 <span class="hljs-keyword">desc</span> 升序 <span class="hljs-keyword">asc</span> 降序<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="截取"><a href="#截取" class="headerlink" title="截取"></a>截取</h4><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql">limit 截取 limit num1 截取开始的位置，num2<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="查看表中的所有列"><a href="#查看表中的所有列" class="headerlink" title="查看表中的所有列"></a>查看表中的所有列</h4><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">select</span> <span class="hljs-operator">*</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> table_name；<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="查看表中的单列-某一列"><a href="#查看表中的单列-某一列" class="headerlink" title="查看表中的单列(某一列)"></a>查看表中的单列(某一列)</h4><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">select</span> _name <span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> table_name；<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="创建存储过程-函数"><a href="#创建存储过程-函数" class="headerlink" title="创建存储过程(函数)"></a>创建存储过程(函数)</h3><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql">delimiter$$将休止符换为$<br>(;变为$)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql">delimiter $$<br><span class="hljs-keyword">create</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">procedure</span> a (xh <span class="hljs-type">char</span>(<span class="hljs-number">12</span>),kch <span class="hljs-type">char</span>(<span class="hljs-number">8</span>))<br><span class="hljs-keyword">begin</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">select</span> grade <span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> grade <span class="hljs-keyword">where</span><br>studentid <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> xh<br><span class="hljs-keyword">and</span> courseid <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> kch;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">end</span> $$<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">call</span> a (<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;St01090100010&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Dp010001&#x27;</span>) $$ <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="创建一个触发器"><a href="#创建一个触发器" class="headerlink" title="创建一个触发器"></a>创建一个触发器</h3><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">create</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">trigger</span> grade_alter after <br>updata <span class="hljs-keyword">on</span> student <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">each</span> <span class="hljs-type">row</span>(<span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">each</span> <span class="hljs-type">row</span> 触发条件为只要修改了一行)<br>updata grade<br><span class="hljs-keyword">set</span> studentid <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> new.studentid<br><span class="hljs-keyword">where</span> studentid <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> old.studentid<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="drop与delete的区别："><a href="#drop与delete的区别：" class="headerlink" title="drop与delete的区别："></a>drop与delete的区别：</h3><h4 id="初学sql语言，难免被drop和delete用法弄混，二者都有删除的意思。那它们又有什么区别呢？"><a href="#初学sql语言，难免被drop和delete用法弄混，二者都有删除的意思。那它们又有什么区别呢？" class="headerlink" title="初学sql语言，难免被drop和delete用法弄混，二者都有删除的意思。那它们又有什么区别呢？"></a>初学sql语言，难免被drop和delete用法弄混，二者都有删除的意思。那它们又有什么区别呢？</h4><ol><li><p>drop主要用于删除结构<br> 例如删除数据库：drop database XX，删除表 drop table XX。字段也是结构的一种，也可以使用drop了？对的，但是我们改变了表结构要先alter方法。例如，我们要删除student表上的age字段的信息，可以这样写：alter table student drop age</p></li><li><p>delete主要用于删除数据<br> 举个例子，要删除 student表上名字为‘张三’的所有信息：delete * from student where name=‘张三’。这种情况下用delete，由此可见delete常用于删除数据。</p></li></ol><h3 id="修改密码"><a href="#修改密码" class="headerlink" title="修改密码"></a>修改密码</h3><ol><li><p>打开终端停止mysql</p> <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ mysql.server stop<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>跳过登陆方式启动并进入mysql</p> <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ sudo mysqld_safe --user=mysql --skip-grant-tables --skip-networking<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>另开一个终端窗口，直接回车进入</p> <figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql">use mysql;<br>FLUSH PRIVILEGES; <br><span class="hljs-keyword">ALTER</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">user</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;root&#x27;</span>@<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;localhost&#x27;</span> IDENTIFIED <span class="hljs-keyword">BY</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;newpassward&#x27;</span><span class="hljs-operator">/</span><span class="hljs-operator">/</span>注意，这里的密码要用包含<span class="hljs-number">8</span>位大写<span class="hljs-operator">+</span>小写<span class="hljs-operator">+</span>特殊字符<span class="hljs-operator">+</span>数字的密码会提示修改密码成功！<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h3 id="导入表"><a href="#导入表" class="headerlink" title="导入表"></a>导入表</h3><ol><li><p>建一个空的数据库</p> <figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">create</span> database datebase_name;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>导入数据库</p> <figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql">use datebase_name;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>设置数据库编码</p> <figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">set</span> names utf8;(可以不用)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>导入数据</p> <figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql">source <span class="hljs-operator">/</span>....<span class="hljs-operator">/</span>xxx.sql<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h3 id="sql语句"><a href="#sql语句" class="headerlink" title="sql语句"></a>sql语句</h3><h4 id="Create"><a href="#Create" class="headerlink" title="Create:"></a>Create:</h4><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">Create</span>:<br><span class="hljs-keyword">Create</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">table</span> table_name (<br>Name1 type1 auto_increment primarykey <span class="hljs-keyword">not</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">null</span>, (主键一定为<span class="hljs-keyword">not</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">null</span>)(自增，主键，非空)<br>Name2 type2 <span class="hljs-keyword">foreign</span> key (外键)<br>);<br><span class="hljs-keyword">Unique</span> 唯一<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="Drop"><a href="#Drop" class="headerlink" title="Drop:"></a>Drop:</h4><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">drop</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">table</span> table_name;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="Alter"><a href="#Alter" class="headerlink" title="Alter:"></a>Alter:</h4><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">alter</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">table</span> table_name <span class="hljs-keyword">add</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">column</span> new_column_name <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">null</span>; 增加新列<br><span class="hljs-keyword">alter</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">table</span> table_name change old_column_name new_column_name <span class="hljs-type">int</span>; 修改列名<br><span class="hljs-keyword">alter</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">table</span> table_name modify column_name <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">not</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">null</span>; 修改数据类型<br><span class="hljs-keyword">alter</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">table</span> table_name rename <span class="hljs-keyword">to</span> new_table_name; 修改表名字<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="Insert"><a href="#Insert" class="headerlink" title="Insert:"></a>Insert:</h4><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">Insert</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">into</span> table_name <span class="hljs-keyword">values</span>(name1 type1 <span class="hljs-keyword">not</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">null</span>); 插入一条数据<br><span class="hljs-operator">/</span><span class="hljs-operator">/</span>多条数据<span class="hljs-operator">+</span><span class="hljs-string">&#x27;,&#x27;</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">Insert</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">into</span> student1 <span class="hljs-keyword">select</span> <span class="hljs-operator">*</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> student;插入一个表中的全部数据<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="Update"><a href="#Update" class="headerlink" title="Update:"></a>Update:</h4><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql">Update table_name <span class="hljs-keyword">set</span> column_name <span class="hljs-operator">=</span><span class="hljs-string">&#x27;修改后的数据&#x27;</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">where</span> column_name <span class="hljs-operator">=</span><span class="hljs-string">&#x27;要修改哪里的数据&#x27;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="Delete"><a href="#Delete" class="headerlink" title="Delete:"></a>Delete:</h4><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">Delete</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> table_name <span class="hljs-keyword">where</span> column_name <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;要删除哪里的数据&#x27;</span> (整行)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="聚集函数"><a href="#聚集函数" class="headerlink" title="聚集函数"></a>聚集函数</h2><h4 id="聚集函数-count，avg，min，max，sum"><a href="#聚集函数-count，avg，min，max，sum" class="headerlink" title="聚集函数(count，avg，min，max，sum)"></a>聚集函数(count，avg，min，max，sum)</h4><ol><li><p>聚集函数通常和group by一起用</p></li><li><p>where/having分别用在group by 前后</p></li><li><p>select column_name from table_name where column_name = xxx gourp by xx having xx(having支持聚集函数)</p></li></ol><h5 id="count-计算行数"><a href="#count-计算行数" class="headerlink" title="count = 计算行数"></a>count = 计算行数</h5><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">SELECT</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">COUNT</span>(<span class="hljs-operator">*</span>) <span class="hljs-keyword">FROM</span> table_name;  <span class="hljs-operator">-</span>返回检索行的数目，不论其是否包含<span class="hljs-keyword">NULL</span>值;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">SELECT</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">COUNT</span>(column_name) <span class="hljs-keyword">FROM</span> tab_teacher; <span class="hljs-operator">-</span>返回<span class="hljs-keyword">SELECT</span>语句检索到的行中非<span class="hljs-keyword">NULL</span>值的数目.<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="avg-min-max-sum"><a href="#avg-min-max-sum" class="headerlink" title="avg min max sum"></a>avg min max sum</h5><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">select</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">avg</span>(column_name) <span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> table_name;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">select</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">min</span>(column_name) <span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> table_name;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">select</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">max</span>(column_name) <span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> table_name;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">select</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">sum</span>(column_name) <span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> table_name;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="Like-模糊查询"><a href="#Like-模糊查询" class="headerlink" title="Like 模糊查询"></a>Like 模糊查询</h5><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">LIKE</span> _(一个字符) <span class="hljs-operator">%</span>(多个字符)<br><span class="hljs-keyword">select</span> column_name <span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> table_name <span class="hljs-keyword">where</span> column_name <span class="hljs-keyword">like</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;_X%&#x27;</span>;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="Order-by"><a href="#Order-by" class="headerlink" title="Order by"></a>Order by</h5><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">select</span> column_name <span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> table_name <span class="hljs-keyword">where</span> colunmn_name <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;xx&#x27;</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">order</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">by</span> ACS<span class="hljs-operator">/</span><span class="hljs-keyword">DESC</span>(升序，降序);<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="Between"><a href="#Between" class="headerlink" title="Between"></a>Between</h5><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">SELECT</span> column_name <span class="hljs-keyword">FROM</span> table_name <span class="hljs-keyword">WHERE</span> column_name <span class="hljs-keyword">BETWEEN</span> <span class="hljs-number">10</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">AND</span> <span class="hljs-number">80</span>;<br><span class="hljs-operator">||</span><br>column_name<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;=</span><span class="hljs-number">10</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">AND</span> column_name <span class="hljs-operator">&lt;=</span><span class="hljs-number">80</span>;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="Is-null"><a href="#Is-null" class="headerlink" title="Is null"></a>Is null</h5><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">SELECT</span> column_name <span class="hljs-keyword">FROM</span> table_name <span class="hljs-keyword">WHERE</span> column_name <span class="hljs-keyword">is</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">null</span> <br><span class="hljs-operator">||</span><br>是否有空值<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="Distinct-去重复"><a href="#Distinct-去重复" class="headerlink" title="Distinct = 去重复"></a>Distinct = 去重复</h5><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">SELECT</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">DISTINCT</span> column_name <span class="hljs-keyword">FROM</span> teble_name<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="Exists-存在"><a href="#Exists-存在" class="headerlink" title="Exists = 存在"></a>Exists = 存在</h5>]]></content>
    
    
    
